---
description: Append parked/later ideas to deferred-ideas store
alwaysApply: true
---

When you recommend something that is **not relevant now** or **useful later**, append it with:

```bash
ftse-defer add --category not_now|later|security|both --title "…" --summary "…" --revisit-when "…" --section learning|universe|research|ops|not_now|security
```

Do not hand-edit `docs/deferred-review.md`. Deduping is by title. See `AGENTS.md`.
